          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Preventing Illegal Immigrants From Abusing Tax Welfare Act of 2015</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) deny the earned income tax credit to any individual who is not a citizen or lawful permanent resident of the United States, and (2) require any taxpayer who is claiming the refundable portion of the child tax credit to provide&nbsp;the social security number of such taxpayer and of each qualifying child to whom a credit is allowed.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2015-07-07T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
